    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan or wok (preferably non-stick) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> over a high heat</p><p>Once hot, add the <strong>sliced garlic</strong>,<strong> chopped pepper</strong> and <strong>mangetout</strong> and cook for 3-4 min or until the vegetables start to soften</p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
