    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the vegetables have softened, add the <strong>meat-free chick’n</strong> with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong> and cook for 2-3 min or until the meat-free chick'n is warmed through</p>",
      "order": 5,
