    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine the <strong>cornflour</strong> with 150ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>cold water</strong> in a small bowl</p><p>Add the <strong>chilli relish</strong>, <strong>soy sauce</strong> and <strong>cornflour mix</strong> to the pan and cook for 3-4 min or until the sauce has thickened – this is your <strong>sweet chilli meat-free chick’n stir-fry</strong></p>",
